{"TopicId":125152,"ForumId":18,"TopicTitle":"How to get to space","CreatedByName":"Glaran K\u0026#039;erman","CreatedById":146334,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-11-12T00:30:10Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Glaran K\u0026#039;erman","CreatedById":146334,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-11-12T00:30:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI am almost certain this guy plays KSP,\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ciframe width=\u0022480\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/2p_8gx-XHJo?feature=oembed\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIt gets hilarious when it starts explaining rockets......\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bill Phil","CreatedById":127797,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-11-12T00:43:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ERandall Munroe(xkcd) has played it.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"CAKE99","CreatedById":150099,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-11-12T01:40:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHere\u0027s a xkcd about KSP\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022https://imgs.xkcd.com/comics/orbital_mechanics.png\u0022 alt=\u0022orbital_mechanics.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Glaran K\u0026#039;erman","CreatedById":146334,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-11-12T13:44:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EBoth awesome!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"viktor19","CreatedById":111560,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-11-14T16:08:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ESpace is hour-and-a-half\u0027s drive away, provided that you have a car that can drive vertically.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Pixel of Life","CreatedById":45646,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-11-14T16:15:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022viktor19\u0022 data-cite=\u0022viktor19\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003ESpace is hour-and-a-half\u0027s drive away, provided that you have a car that can drive vertically.\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAn hour and a half? How low are the speed limits over there in Croatia? I could get to space in about 45 mins (60 if winter speed limits are in effect).\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bill Phil","CreatedById":127797,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-11-14T18:54:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022CaptainKorhonen\u0022 data-cite=\u0022CaptainKorhonen\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EAn hour and a half? How low are the speed limits over there in Croatia? I could get to space in about 45 mins (60 if winter speed limits are in effect).\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI think he means beyond the Karman Line.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"viktor19","CreatedById":111560,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-11-14T21:31:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022CaptainKorhonen\u0022 data-cite=\u0022CaptainKorhonen\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EAn hour and a half? How low are the speed limits over there in Croatia? I could get to space in about 45 mins (60 if winter speed limits are in effect).\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHighest speed limit is 130 km/h on highways. It depends what altitude you take for space.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Pixel of Life","CreatedById":45646,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-11-14T21:59:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Bill Phil\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Bill Phil\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EI think he means beyond the Karman Line.\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003ESo do I. The summer speed limit on our highways is 120 km/h. At that speed the 100km trip would take exactly 50 minutes.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bill Phil","CreatedById":127797,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-11-14T22:29:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022CaptainKorhonen\u0022 data-cite=\u0022CaptainKorhonen\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003ESo do I. The summer speed limit on our highways is 120 km/h. At that speed the 100km trip would take exactly 50 minutes.\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EBut beyond would take much more time. Say... 120 km. An hour. 240 km altitude, pretty common for LEO, 2 hours. 100 km is at the Karman Line, not quite beyond.\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}